here. We got a nice lot of - Buff Orpingtons. And White Winedots. And Sealy Campions. And I reared quite a lot of chickens that way. I - did quite a good trade as well. And the power - the power station was being built on our fields do you see, so we had 
plenty of - eggs, the customers
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10968918 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14815767\charrsid15934717 Because you saw the area altering didn't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1406435 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14815767\charrsid15934717 Oh I did, yes, I remember before a brick of the power station was built. I remember the laying of the foundation stone.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10968918 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14815767\charrsid15934717 It was quite when you were a little girl was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1406435 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14815767\charrsid15934717 Very quiet, yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10968918 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14815767\charrsid15934717 Would your father have anything else on the farm, other animals?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1406435 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14815767\charrsid15934717 Well - he - he - of course a farm is rotation, you've got calves, then they come to }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid5642835\charrsid15934717 B}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14815767\charrsid15934717 eheifers and - it's the world do you see - yearlings do you see then - then milking cows. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10968918 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14815767\charrsid15934717 Would he grow anything like wheat or barl}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5642835\charrsid15934717 e}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid14815767\charrsid15934717 y?
