\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5642835\charrsid15934717 n}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14815767\charrsid15934717  - had sugar with it. So that's it. What else did you ask?
