 said, os'a master? He says, ydych in dod ir cwrdd? Odw. Righ, chin gallu cael cino gyda pregethwr, and he used to come up the - to the upper room as I say now, and we'd have dinner together, the preacher, the serving men and father, me - all of us do you
 see.
