\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1406435 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14815767\charrsid15934717 No, no. I remember - cabbage now, very - limited cabbage. Very. There was plenty of it there mind, but - os na ti moyna gade.
