 thought a lot of my father. Mm. Yes, he'd never put a finger on one of us. Never. Isn't it nice to think of that? Yes. But mother made up for it. Yes. Well - she knew the way to tell us off anyway. Yes. But it was good, she had a family to see to do you 
see.
