enarth. Yes. Down to Penarth we saw the - and we used to go to Barry. My eldest sister - lived in Barry for years, the eldest of father's children, you see, Hannah.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10968918 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14815767\charrsid15934717 She was very much older than you wasn't she?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1406435 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14815767\charrsid15934717 Yes. Yes. Very much, yes. Until we 
used to go and visit her and go down to the seaside-, and we used to go to Penarth, I had an Aunt Florrie there, she was there and she was - we used to go down there regular.
\par 
