\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1406435 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14815767\charrsid15934717 Oh well that was when we - fetched - we had to fetch extra water Saturday 'cos we daren't fetch it on Sunday. Oh no, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10968918 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14815767\charrsid15934717 What if you were desperate?
