Well we would have to drink with the rain water. If it came - yes. And no - there was no dust, no we wouldn't we - if we picked a blackberry - hm - you were - all right, all right, we'll remember this. And
 there were some punishments, goodness knows - it wouldn't be much perhaps but it was punishment, yes. Perhaps it was you had to be without seeing your little periodical 'til the next week, you know, something small like that do you see, yes. And always t
h
ey'd all - any - we prepared our - our Sunday more or less started Saturday night. Because we used to do all the potatoes peeling, cabbage cleaning or anything, they were all done Saturday. I do it now. I never do it on Sunday. Cake making - yes, it's bee
n - it's been instilled in us, we can't do different. No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10968918 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14815767\charrsid15934717 What about Sundays then, how would you spend Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1406435 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14815767\charrsid15934717 Well - always had to make of course and wash up and - and milk utensils, you see the buckets and - the milk had to go away Sunday m
orning like some other morning. And get ready after and we used to go to chapel and one of us would stay home, you see, and then to see to the dinner. And the others to go to chapel. Then come home to dinner, off to Sunday school after, come back and - co
me and milk, then I'd be off after to - be at Singing school after at quarter past five, 'til six o'clock and then the service. That's - that's our life on Sunday.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10968918 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14815767\charrsid15934717 It was busy wasn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1406435 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14815767\charrsid15934717 Yes. Yes. Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10968918 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14815767\charrsid15934717 Did you play games?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1406435 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14815767\charrsid15934717 Not on Sunday. Oh no.
