irs paid and we-d order a hamper full of food, and we'd take a place in just by the triangle in Barry, we went there several times, and - the - girls of our church - two or three of my older sisters would be serving up the tea do you see, and the food you
 see, we'd have a loan of the - cutle}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12585436\charrsid15934717 ry and the sitting down like se}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14815767\charrsid15934717 e.
