\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1406435 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14815767\charrsid15934717 Yes.
 Yes, from Saron, Treforest. And they went from Saron to St Davids, 'cos there was a pipe organ at St Davids for her to play it do you see. Well now, she - and she had a nice voice too. And we used to have singing festivals. My husband - well, you would s
ee it in that report I think you might see it there, it was he conducted ever gmanfa of the - of the gymanfa for forty-three years without a break..
