to - other - we were beginners you know, yes, well I know - I remember there was a bit of a row, and I used to try then - I tried in Salem Llantwit and at John Hughes, the Capel Rhondda, do you see. Then I tried in Castellau and T.D. Edwardes. Oh I've don
e a lot of something. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10968918 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14815767\charrsid15934717 Did the chapel run any temperance club?
