No, not as a Band of Hope. It was - it was a Band of Hope - that my husband - Band of Hope - gamanfa it was. Band of Hope festival, so we learnt everything - everything - what do you say now, dirwest - temperance, dirwest you see, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10968918 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14815767\charrsid15934717 Did you have a Band of Hope in the chapel?
