Yes. I had my mother - taking part. Yes. But - but she - she'd do it, yes, yes. I wish if I could do it but I can't I'm sorry. Well I haven't got the - I don't know - I'm afraid I'd go too personal or something, and that's nothing to a
nybody else, you know.
\par 
