On - occasions, it all depends now, well my mother might say - look here, look how well catered we are for this now, don't you think that one of you - your daddy would perhaps you s
ee, yes. Yes. But we girls, we've taught our children to do it, and I've - I've asked to grace at - at meals you know, I've done that. Through and through with other people see, you can take your turn.
