Well it all depends the man perhaps if he was rather ol he wouldn't bother you see. No. If it was - yes, yes, some had a way of it, they - they - you come into it, you can't help it, you know, he comes in.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10968918 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14815767\charrsid15934717 Would you have it when the minister wasn't there?
