 think. He was a red-hot liberal, I know that. And he was a Guardian, he was on the council in - in - yes, yes, yes, yes, he was -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10968918 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14815767\charrsid15934717 Why do you think he was a Liberal?
