re was no spare time with children. No. No. No. But I must say - we are - we were well dressed in everything. Everything, yes, because - you know it was a lot of things I know - in the - in the herb line I know. About - Southernwood - after - that was a v
e
ry - thing that my father used to gather, wash and put it in a jug of boiling water and he'd drink it occasionally. It was good for the back. Yes, and a spot of wormwood perhaps would be in it you see. Southernwood yes. Risgan lwyd it is in Welsh. Mm, wor
