I was - we were married on the fourth - on the fifth of - fifth of March, fifth of March, and I - I was twenty-six and I was twenty-seven the end of March, a fortnight -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10968918 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14815767\charrsid15934717 Married?
