\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10968918 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14815767\charrsid15934717 That was quite a long time before wasn't it?
