\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1406435 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14815767\charrsid15934717 Yes, what could I be, I was a schoolgirl. Schoolgirl then you see, I little thought that he - I'd ever marry him do yo
