 went up to Cilfynydd, Cilfynydd he was living then, and she went up for about two years. And then we had a - this festival for a children}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15417729\charrsid15934717 \rquote }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
