 solo with one of the little Band of Hope children, or a recitation or something like that. And in the second - gamanfa, Miss Morfudd Owen sang there. And she was the first to sing, but in the following gamanfa I sang. Yes. And by then I had been a pupil 
for his for a twelve month, you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10968918 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14815767\charrsid15934717 Where did Mr Jenkins come from?
