\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14815767\charrsid15934717 edici collar, stuck up this way you know, oh it was - and - and a - a - white fox cape on my shoulders, head, animal, all do you see, yes. Yes. And black shoes a
nd stockings, black, but my frock was ankle length, you couldn't see much under see. But they weren't these - they didn't have the fancy shoe then see. Yes.
