 wonderful - I need a pound, it was a pound for him and he got it, I - you know, the only thing he did was smoke, but not to an extent, because there - there was a period - he left it off for his own good, then he went back to it, then he went - he left o
ff after 'cos he went to the optician, he said, you are a smoker, so you'd better leave off smoking and come to me in six months. He didn't go back to him for a couple of years, because he had got better do you see, and didn't require him.
