nd I and her were there do you see and I was - all - was in perfect health you might say. Until about - about six weeks before the baby came I fell. On the top of the stair. There was a - you - step to go down and step to go up to the back bedroom. Someho
w I didn't negotiate those, I fell, I didn't go all the way down the stair, but I had an awful jerk. Awful jerk and then I - I had - I had a woman to do my washing, and she came in and did it for the week or two before. Like that.
